ly.img.android.pesdk.backend.filter

Class FilterAsset

  • java.lang.Object
    • ly.img.android.pesdk.backend.model.config.AbstractAsset
      • ly.img.android.pesdk.backend.filter.FilterAsset
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DuotoneFilterAsset, FilterAssetHatch, LutColorFilterAsset

    public class FilterAsset
extends AbstractAsset
    Represents the Image-Filter base file. For Camera live Preview the filter is OpenGl Based but has also a Renderscript implementation to triggerOperatorsIfNeeded final images in full resolution.
